<assessment id="u3_m3_bridge1_tutor2">
   <title>Tutor</title>
   <question id="q1">
      <body>
         <p>What is the probability that a student
            <?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111724-0500"?>will
            <?oxy_insert_end?>change<?oxy_delete author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111727-0500" content="s"?>
            majors at least once? </p>
      </body>
      <short_answer id="A"/>
      <part>
         <response input="A" match="*" score="1"/>
         <explanation>
            <p>The phrase “at least once” means 1 or more times. The easiest way to calculate this is P(a student changes majors at least once) = 1 – P(X=0) = 1 – 0.135 = 0.865
            </p>
            <p>Of
               course<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111747-0500"?>,<?oxy_insert_end?>
               you could also add 0.271<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111749-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>+<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111811-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>0.271<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111813-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>+<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111814-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>0.180<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111816-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>+<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111816-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>0.090<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111817-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>+<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111818-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>0.036<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111819-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>+<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111820-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>0.012<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111821-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>+<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111822-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>0.003<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111824-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>+<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111824-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>0.002<?oxy_insert_start author="mmyers" timestamp="20101120T111826-0500"?>
               <?oxy_insert_end?>= 0.865 </p>
         </explanation>
